<![CDATA[<font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi&nbsp;{!Account.Client_First_Name__c},<br><br>We’re excited to offer you the ability to connect your Facebook Business Page to your Lead Stream dashboard. This means you can easily post status updates, reviews, offers, and photos to your news feed.&nbsp; Here are the steps to connect:&nbsp;</font><div><br></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">1. Log in at </span><a href="https://dashboard.web.com" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">dashboard.web.com</a><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">.</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">2. Select the menu icon on the top left.&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">3. Click Web Presence, then Social.</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">4. Hit Connect to Facebook.</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">5. You will see a few prompts asking if you want Web.com to post on your page. Check off the box on the bottom and click through each prompt.</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">6. A list of pages that we’ve found that may match your business will appear. Click on the one that matches your business and hit Complete Setup. If you don’t see your business listed click on None of These.</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">7. Confirm the information shown is accurate and then click Complete Setup.</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><br></span><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">That's all! Now any photos you upload, offers you create, or reviews you receive will automatically be posted to your page. If you have any questions, please let us know!</font><div><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Thank you for choosing Web.com. We appreciate your business!</span></div><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span id="j_id0:j_id8"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"></font></span></p><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">{!User.FirstName}</span></div><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Lead Stream Support</span></div><div><span id="j_id0:j_id8" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span id="j_id0:j_id8:j_id9:j_id246:j_id248:1:j_id249:j_id250" style=""><div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">(888) 599-2656</font></div><div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font style="" size="2">leadstreamsupport@web.com</font></div></span></span></div></div>]]></td>
